  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/peripherals/\" rel=\"tag\">外围设备</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/07/canopy-sensus-app-enhancing-case/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/c982fcbcb862212a35db5e89b0bf208/ces_2014_canopy_sensus_main.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n去年 CES 时我们曾动手玩过 Canopy 的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/01/06/canopy-sensus-iphone-chinese-hands-on/\">Sensus</a> 触控保护套，今年他们再度光临赌城，也带来了全新的产品。公司软件工程副总裁 Joel Stewart 早些时候为我们做了示范，据悉他们这次针对 Lightning 接口进行了修改，而且在产品设计方面也做了相当大的改动。原先背面和侧边的触控板现在被换成了压力感应垫，能在应用内实现的功能也随之有了变化。比如说，现在你可以把套着 Sensus 的手机翻过来放在桌上，然后放上一样物体，特定的 App 就能准确说出它的重量。下面为大家附上动手玩图集，视频跳转后就可以看到了。<br />\n<div class=\"postgallery\"><p><strong>Gallery: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/canopys-sensus-app-enhancing-case-hands-on/\">Canopy's Sensus app enhancing case hands-on</a></strong></p><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/canopys-sensus-app-enhancing-case-hands-on/6431214/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/ces-2014-canopy-sensus00-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/canopys-sensus-app-enhancing-case-hands-on/6431215/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/ces-2014-canopy-sensus01-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/canopys-sensus-app-enhancing-case-hands-on/6431216/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/ces-2014-canopy-sensus02-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/canopys-sensus-app-enhancing-case-hands-on/6431217/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/01/ces-2014-canopy-sensus03-1_thumbnail.jpg\" title=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/photos/canopys-sensus-app-enhancing-case-hands-on/6431218/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2014/